data.description: Welcome to your very own hobby farm in North Western Jay County! This home sits on 4 acres and contains many outdoor buildings. A large 3 car detached garage with cement floors can be used for storage and a workshop. The other buildings are good for storage and animals. The home is heated and cooled by geothermal with a wood burning stove for back up heat. This home has been updated by the current owner. The kitchen and bathroom have received a complete remodel. This 3 bed, 2 bath is waiting for new owners to experience all it has to offer.
